query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(it mi mc) NoMergeJoin(it mc mi ct) NoHashJoin(ct it mc mi t) */ select min(t.title) AS american_movie
from info_type AS it
inner join movie_info AS mi
on it.id = mi.info_type_id AND mi.info IN ('America',
'English',
'German',
'Norwegian',
'Swedish',
'Denmark',
'Danish',
'American',
'USA',
'Bulgaria')
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.note not like '%(TV)%' AND mc.note like '%(USA)%'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1995;
